{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六章「假仁假义」：阿飞潜入柴房救李寻欢，却落入田七、赵正义等人设下的陷阱。游龙生以貂裘伪装诱敌，十几名弩手围困阿飞，赵正义趁机偷袭。阿飞夺剑突围，身受重伤后在雪地逃亡，被铁笛先生截住。铁笛先生以铁笛功击伤阿飞双腿，却在听到同伙赶来时放阿飞离去。阿飞在雪地中艰难前行，想起李寻欢的嘱托，拼尽最后一口气。与此同时，龙啸云将李寻欢从柴房搬至屋内照料，表面嘘寒问暖，李寻欢却洞悉其伪善本质，以幽默口吻拒绝解开穴道，暗含对龙啸云的宽容与无奈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "阁下还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请动手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "好，阁下倒不愧是个痛快的人，田某就索性成全了你吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这少年好快的身手！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "他的运气也不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "运气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "少庄主方才难道未瞧见他身上已挨了两箭么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "不错，我已看出他左手舞剑，剑光中仍有破绽，必定挡不住七爷属下的神弩，奇怪的是，他居然没有受伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "这只因他身上穿了金丝甲，我千算万算，竟忘了这一着，否则他纵有天大的本事，今日也休想能活着走出这间柴屋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他今天不该来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "胜负兵家常事，少庄主又何必懊恼？何况，那厮纵然闯过了我们这一关，第二关他还能闯得过去么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出家人原来也会打埋伏。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "老僧并无伤人之心，檀越何必逞口舌之利，需知利在口舌，损在心头，不能伤人，陡伤自己。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "和尚的口舌之利，似乎也不在檀越之下吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "出家人不愿杀生，檀越你掌中有剑，脚下有足，只要能冲得出老僧这小小的罗汉门，老僧便心悦诚服，恭送如仪。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "檀越难道想束手就缚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "既不愿就缚，为何不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "你不杀我，我也不能杀你，就冲不出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "檀越若能杀得了老僧，老僧死而无怨。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "檀越慢走，老僧相送。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_cha_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "胡碴僧人",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_hu_cha_seng_ren",
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少年僧人",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "他已逃不远了，师叔为何要放他逃走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian_seng_ren",
      "text": "他既已逃不远了，为何还要追？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少年僧人",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "师叔说得是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出家人慈悲为怀，能不伤人，还是不伤人的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个出家人慈悲为怀，若有别人替他杀人，他自己就不肯动手了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "铁笛先生？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你受了伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "伤在背后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你已看出，何必再问？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是心眉和尚下的手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少林护法原来也不过如此。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "以他的身份，本不该在背后出手伤人，既已伤了你，便不该还让你能活着走到我面前。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老和尚难道是想借刀杀人么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我告诉你三件事，第一，若不在背后出手，他根本出不了手，第二，他纵然出手也杀不死我，第三，你更杀不死我！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "少年人好大的口气。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你既已受伤，我本不愿出手，但你的口气太大，我不能不教训你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "念在你已受伤，我让你三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "既已见到了我，你还想走？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我不走，你就得死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是我死，还是你死？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "没有人能让我三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我若让你三招，就非死不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你为何不试试？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人能让我三招，一招都不能！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但你没有死，也因为你让我三招，你没有失信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你至少比心眉强得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "还有两招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "还有两招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我让你三招，你只出手一招。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "今天我已学会了一件事，绝不让任何人三招，你也该学会一件事……若要出手，就一定要令对方倒下，否则你就绝不要出手！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这件事我一定忘不了的！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈，铁老前辈，你得手了么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_di_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁笛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走，我已无力杀你，也不愿你死在别人手上！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥，你看我一滴酒都没有漏出来吧，我就算被人悬空倒着吊起来，但若有人喂我喝酒，我也绝不会漏出来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为什么不让我解开你的穴道？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我是个禁不起诱惑的人，你若解开我的穴道，我说不定就想跑了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在……现在他们都不在这里，你若……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥，你到现在还不明白我的意思么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我明白，可是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道你又想说那句话了，但你实在并没有什么对不起我的地方，你将我从柴房搬到这里来，又有酒喝，这已不亏我们兄弟一场了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    }
